the listener experience

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:03.200
the creative process
of an artist that

00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:06.030
wants to communicate his
music in a different way.

00:05:06.030 --> 00:05:10.970
And in stereo, it's fine,
and on an iPod, it's fine.

00:05:10.970 --> 00:05:12.360
On headphones, it's fine.

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:16.260
But this, you actually
put inside the music

00:05:16.260 --> 00:05:18.860
that the guy
created, or the girl,

00:05:18.860 --> 00:05:22.470
and you live the
emotional experience,

00:05:22.470 --> 00:05:25.090
which is so much
bigger and so much more

00:05:25.090 --> 00:05:29.434
involved with yourself than
just listening to two speakers.

00:05:29.434 --> 00:05:31.850
MATTHEW HENDERSHOT: So you
