00:44:33.330 --> 00:44:39.070
So it's not mapped encoding like
there is Dolby or DTS, where

00:44:39.070 --> 00:44:41.020
you have grids where
you map your speakers

00:44:41.020 --> 00:44:42.320
in certain places.

00:44:42.320 --> 00:44:44.310
But that gives timing issues.

00:44:44.310 --> 00:44:47.000
This is a discrete
system in that sense,

00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:49.060
and like I said,
easier to integrate

00:44:49.060 --> 00:44:53.252
into the home than
more speakers.

00:44:53.252 --> 00:44:54.210
MATTHEW HENDERSHOT: OK.

