But binaural--

00:48:13.248 --> 00:48:15.160
AUDIENCE: Yeah, that's the on.

00:48:15.160 --> 00:48:16.976
RONALD PRENT: Technology.

00:48:16.976 --> 00:48:20.230
But it gives you the feel
that you're very isolated

00:48:20.230 --> 00:48:21.139
in your headphones.

00:48:21.139 --> 00:48:22.680
That's why some
people didn't like it

00:48:22.680 --> 00:48:24.600
and other people like it.

